Actions.Text: REFERRED TO CORPORATIONS, AUTHORITIES AND COMMISSIONS
REFERRED TO CORPORATIONS, AUTHORITIES AND COMMISSIONS

Title: Relates to retiring cemetery indebtedness
Summary: Provides for the reversion of certain unclaimed assets to the cemetery corporation's permanent maintenance fund for the preservation, improvement and maintenance of the cemetery.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the not-for-profit corporation law, in relation to retiring cemetery indebtedness
